  <summary date="2016-06-07T04:00:00Z" status="Introduced in House">Medicare Dental, Vision, and Hearing Benefit Act of 2016

This bill amends title XVIII (Medicare) of the Social Security Act to provide for Medicare coverage of dental, vision, and hearing care. With respect to such care, the bill establishes special payment rules, limitations, and coinsurance requirements.</summary>
